definition:
Someone descended from Mahli who was a man of the tribe of Levi living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Exo.6.19; 
 son of: Merari (H4847); 
 brother of: Mushi (H4187) and Jaaziah (H3269); 
 father of: Libni (H3845H), Eleazar (H0499J) and Kish (H7027H)
Group of mach.li (מַחְלִי "Mahli" H4249) 
 § Mahlites, of Mahli "my sickness"
 descendants of Mahli, the grandson of Levi
